"    Two-dimensional transthoracic echocardiogram (2D TTE) from the parasternal short axis view showing the papillary muscles",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"cntnt\" style=\"width: 380px; height: 257px; background-image: url(data:image/jpeg;base64,);\">",
